{"tid":35233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港既「市區」同「近郊」應該點定義?","createTime":"2016-12-12T03:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T14:51:17.000Z","uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e3db68e628221530fbc878b0e7295a2f8807137","tid":35233,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:02:26.000Z","msg":"新界屬於近郊，港九屬於市區，呢個應該冇咩異議<br />\n<br />\n但係有D地區例如荃灣、葵青、將軍澳雖然係喺新界，但係地理上好接近市區，而且又有地鐵到，發展上同市區幾乎融為一體，呢D地區可唔可以視為市區既一部分？<br />\n<br />\n又例如香港仔、鴨脷洲雖然係喺港島，但係同港島北鬧市始終隔左一段距離，而且以住宅為主，商業活動相對較少，呢D地區仲應唔應該視為市區？"},{"pid":"1ab7d48bffedc341b7557814a9aca22a2813cdd4","tid":35233,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:11:17.000Z","msg":"南區真係完全唔可以計落市區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n赤柱 深水灣果啲同中環金鐘完全係兩個世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"914f473498e0b7584c14facf5038ee60ce029f8c","tid":35233,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:13:07.000Z","msg":"油尖旺銅金灣中上 半小時生活圈=市區"},{"pid":"82fd23cb763b4cb276e006f9006ac246af121326","tid":35233,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:15:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>油尖旺銅金灣中上 半小時生活圈=市區</blockquote><br />\n新線通車之後，黃竹坑/鴨脷洲去油尖旺銅金灣中上都係半個鐘左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22fc41e2563e8a7dfc5a4c3f88901c45fb920c8a","tid":35233,"uid":22196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:19:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>油尖旺銅金灣中上 半小時生活圈=市區</blockquote><br />\n新線通車之後，黃竹坑/鴨脷洲去油尖旺銅金灣中上都係半個鐘左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n南區出銅鑼灣灣仔金鐘最快可以兩個字內 路路暢通既話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時行西隧出油麻地旺角其實都好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e40ff1a0a1f884e7d8ead7e47d7590a1362267","tid":35233,"uid":45872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:23:49.000Z","msg":"新界唔一定係郊區 港島唔一定係市區"},{"pid":"91e241faed1e3c22a9c971146b42c1941720fbf5","tid":35233,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:30:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新界唔一定係郊區 港島唔一定係市區</blockquote><br />\n我明白唔一定，所以就想討論下D灰色地帶"},{"pid":"bbd7e76761f85faa44f4dec367ca148638cac69b","tid":35233,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:35:47.000Z","msg":"南區,大西北同沙田同市區之間有buffer"},{"pid":"249cbfc8049d75f5c6cf1d6a8abb634e2ef715e9","tid":35233,"uid":39032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:39:33.000Z","msg":"荃灣葵涌市中心應該算市區？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb992367d9c8c3d92df3f27724c994b70dab6e9","tid":35233,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:39:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>南區,大西北同沙田同市區之間有buffer<br />\n將軍澳夠近隧道兩邊都係 build-up area 同等密度, 算市區 </blockquote>"},{"pid":"e74d2fba077eb50ead3093e4e2132cf79d72a4bd","tid":35233,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:44:21.000Z","msg":"天水圍係山區？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db32b158d2430f7e7b644d72c926319483ea3a53","tid":35233,"uid":39032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:44:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/香港市區\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B8%82%E5%8D%80&d=7l2NxX2U2C0wnsvbV6UrZmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=144db76c\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/香港市區</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇Urban專家解釋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2fbeec2e197e39720a81a173e53aee3bc9fbed","tid":35233,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:46:23.000Z","msg":"會唔跟排公屋個市區定義啱？"},{"pid":"1314c888e8c9c23a24c542ce6284fcbc0c631363","tid":35233,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:47:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔跟排公屋個市區定義啱？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我們的公共屋邨分布在全港四個地區：<br />\n<br />\n市區 (包括港島及九龍)<br />\n擴展市區 (包括東涌、沙田、馬鞍山、將軍澳、荃灣、葵涌及青衣)<br />\n新界 (包括屯門、元朗、天水圍、上水、粉嶺及大埔)<br />\n離島 (不包括東涌)"},{"pid":"086cbc07e26ab566872bb194ca51935f483283f2","tid":35233,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:53:41.000Z","msg":"好多人會當荃灣係九龍，以前熊貓酒店叫九龍悅來酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39486ef99c1e70c1d3027f163f3beb262f78e9d0","tid":35233,"uid":11161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:55:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多人會當荃灣係九龍，以前熊貓酒店叫九龍悅來酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成個荃灣都係紅的 真係以為係九龍"},{"pid":"939ce13e35db1d6a34d152adc709d07ae2990294","tid":35233,"uid":39032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:01:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好多人會當荃灣係九龍，以前熊貓酒店叫九龍悅來酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成個荃灣都係紅的 真係以為係九龍</blockquote><br />\n綠的荃灣市中心好似淨係可以停地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"102ae5ec361fe8ff8a9f87eee7ed704aa86a5f3f","tid":35233,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:03:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好多人會當荃灣係九龍，以前熊貓酒店叫九龍悅來酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成個荃灣都係紅的 真係以為係九龍</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實可唔可以係西貢坐綠的去荃灣？"},{"pid":"9c30bf5f3fa1ad114753ba26ac781b2180012e12","tid":35233,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:12:47.000Z","msg":"市政局管嘅就係市區<br />\n區域市政局管嘅就係近郊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新加坡就係鄉下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba17c25330887b6bc3c4734b6894c21f9f0c6f0","tid":35233,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:21:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好多人會當荃灣係九龍，以前熊貓酒店叫九龍悅來酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成個荃灣都係紅的 真係以為係九龍</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實可唔可以係西貢坐綠的去荃灣？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n經馬鞍山應該得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e816c13c2aded887581128840353f776eb8203","tid":35233,"uid":25101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:30:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成個荃灣都係紅的 真係以為係九龍</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實可唔可以係西貢坐綠的去荃灣？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n經馬鞍山應該得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n馬𩣑山屬新界定九龍架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18114e7aa6bf34d6144014544517b56a85d74c3b","tid":35233,"uid":19728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:34:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成個荃灣都係紅的 真係以為係九龍</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實可唔可以係西貢坐綠的去荃灣？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n經馬鞍山應該得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n經馬鞍山 馬場 城門隧道 荃錦交會處(唔識打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 西樓角路去荃灣地鐵站<br />\n呢條路應該得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.